verbose_text: In the context of amino-bisphosphonate drugs, such as ZOL, the gammadelta T cells can produce interferon (IFN)-gamma, TNF-alpha and GM-CSF, which mediate monocyte differentiation to iDCs and induce iDCs to further mature.
evidence: interferon (IFN)-gamma, TNF-alpha and GM-CSF, which mediate monocyte differentiation
